{"tid":743324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國麥當勞沙律疑受污染　6州數十客人感染寄生蟲","createTime":"2018-07-15T10:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T14:56:42.000Z","uid":13468,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ac269e8aa95eeaa25616053e9bc9d1f8f5095008","tid":743324,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T10:16:20.000Z","msg":"美國麥當勞沙律疑受污染　6州數十客人感染寄生蟲<br />\n<br />\n美國6個州的衛生部門公布，發現有人因吃麥當勞的沙律後感染環孢子蟲，當局相信用來製作沙律的生菜是感染來源。麥當勞回應表示，在更換另一家生菜供應商之前，公司有義務暫停供應沙律，現時已與衛生部門聯絡，在美國中西部約3000家門店停售問題沙律。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至今，威斯康辛州、內布拉斯加州與南達科他州均各有2宗個案，明尼蘇達州有3宗，而愛荷華州和伊利諾州則分別有16宗和29宗。<br />\n<br />\n據美國疾病管制及預防中心（CDC）資料顯示，環孢子蟲屬於非致命感染疫病，常見的病徵為水狀腹瀉，平均在進食後的第7日出現病徵。<br />\n<br />\n(今日美國)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180714/s00005/1531540773798\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180714%2Fs00005%2F1531540773798&d=y1ExX8AUYFFJkpHQSQ5RNZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=6b8622b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180714%2Fs00005%2F1531540773798&h=265273a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180714/s00005/1531540773798</a>"},{"pid":"f96d3ae8d2376d344d68c22a544e395ab5217628","tid":743324,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T13:53:27.000Z","msg":"又係金拱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef06fbbcdb7aadae60c445d54ca11fb9d4066fd","tid":743324,"uid":164913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T14:18:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7623858a16b9b1704f2a52d954404d368e50325","tid":743324,"uid":36993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eef06fbbcdb7aadae60c445d54ca11fb9d4066fd","tid":743324,"uid":164913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f96d3ae8d2376d344d68c22a544e395ab5217628","tid":